[
  {
    "startTime": 5.547,
    "endTime": 6.757,
    "text": "Yellow?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.466,
    "endTime": 8.759,
    "text": "Pink?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.427,
    "endTime": 13.138,
    "text": "You do care!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.601,
    "endTime": 20.354,
    "text": "Let's promise to never fight again, buddy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.521,
    "endTime": 22.898,
    "text": "Yeah, pal. Let's go home."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.277,
    "endTime": 29.029,
    "text": "Hey, where ya going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.279,
    "endTime": 31.782,
    "text": "Get back here and kill each other!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.907,
    "endTime": 34.159,
    "text": "You're my best friend ever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.326,
    "endTime": 35.619,
    "text": "You too, Patrick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.036,
    "endTime": 44.294,
    "text": "You know, if I were to die right now, in some sort of fiery explosion due to the carelessness of a friend, well, that would just be OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.339,
    "endTime": 48.423,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.924,
    "endTime": 52.219,
    "text": "Wow, it feels like something just dropped into my lower intestine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.303,
    "endTime": 54.555,
    "text": "Hey, smells like cherry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.888,
    "endTime": 56.89,
    "text": "Or maybe grape? Blueberry?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.015,
    "endTime": 59.852000000000004,
    "text": "Here it is, the sunset!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.935,
    "endTime": 62.187000000000005,
    "text": "I always love to count it down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.312,
    "endTime": 64.73,
    "text": "Five... you do the rest, buddy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.399,
    "endTime": 68.151,
    "text": "Four... three..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.485,
    "endTime": 70.153,
    "text": "Two..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.947,
    "endTime": 72.99000000000001,
    "text": "One!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.991,
    "endTime": 77.202,
    "text": "I guess we started too early! Let's start again!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.203,
    "endTime": 81.915,
    "text": "Five, four, three..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.709,
    "endTime": 87.254,
    "text": "Two, one!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.755,
    "endTime": 94.511,
    "text": "Well, at least I was able to make his last few hours meaningful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.804,
    "endTime": 98.64,
    "text": "I am such a good person."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.765,
    "endTime": 100.392,
    "text": "SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.517,
    "endTime": 102.101,
    "text": "SpongeBob!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.192,
    "endTime": 112.487,
    "text": "You don't have to be a baby to get all of Grandma's love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.405,
    "endTime": 114.44800000000001,
    "text": "I don't?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.698,
    "endTime": 116.116,
    "text": "Of course not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.241,
    "endTime": 121.496,
    "text": "No matter how grown up you get, you will always be my little baby boo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.123,
    "endTime": 127.461,
    "text": "And remember, you can kiss your grandma and still be an adult."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.586,
    "endTime": 129.253,
    "text": "Here you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.548,
    "endTime": 132.883,
    "text": "Thanks, Grandma."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.468,
    "endTime": 137.304,
    "text": "Hold on, Gary! I'm coming!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.429,
    "endTime": 141.808,
    "text": "Uh-oh, one of the coaches seems to have raced onto the track."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.892,
    "endTime": 144.394,
    "text": "That is an automatic disqualification."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.52,
    "endTime": 148.44,
    "text": "Looks like number six has this race all wrapped up, ladies and gentlemen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.565,
    "endTime": 151.859,
    "text": "Come on, Snelly! It's all you, baby!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.985,
    "endTime": 153.94600000000003,
    "text": "Oh Gary, I'm sorry!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.029,
    "endTime": 156.948,
    "text": "Why didn't you just say I was pushing you too hard?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.032,
    "endTime": 157.9,
    "text": "Meow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.9,
    "endTime": 158.61700000000002,
    "text": "You did?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.7,
    "endTime": 162.286,
    "text": "Oh Gary, why didn't you tell me I wasn't listening?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.412,
    "endTime": 163.1,
    "text": "Meow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.1,
    "endTime": 163.74699999999999,
    "text": "You did?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.872,
    "endTime": 167.584,
    "text": "Oh, Gary! Oh, Gary!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.253,
    "endTime": 170.254,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.34,
    "endTime": 174.299,
    "text": "Gary?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.492,
    "endTime": 202.077,
    "text": "It's me, SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.202,
    "endTime": 203.745,
    "text": "We used to work together."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.329,
    "endTime": 205.33,
    "text": "SpongeBob?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.455,
    "endTime": 206.58200000000002,
    "text": "There you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.707,
    "endTime": 207.916,
    "text": "So, where you living these days?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 209.0,
    "text": "Squidward Tentacles?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.0,
    "endTime": 209.751,
    "text": "Yes?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.835,
    "endTime": 210.961,
    "text": "Sign here please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.088,
    "endTime": 214.673,
    "text": "Uh, nowhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.756,
    "endTime": 216.842,
    "text": "Great! And what have you been doing with yourself?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.925,
    "endTime": 218.55200000000002,
    "text": "No wait, let me guess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.303,
    "endTime": 221.305,
    "text": "I see you've been working on that mustache."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.597,
    "endTime": 224.76600000000002,
    "text": "The tattered clothes, the awful smell,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.892,
    "endTime": 226.29999999999998,
    "text": "you're a football player!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.3,
    "endTime": 226.894,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.019,
    "endTime": 228.4,
    "text": "A space man!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.4,
    "endTime": 229.229,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.354,
    "endTime": 231.77300000000002,
    "text": "- A football playing king in space? - Don't you get it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.857,
    "endTime": 235.027,
    "text": "I'm a loser!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.152,
    "endTime": 237.821,
    "text": "I've lost my job, my home."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.155,
    "endTime": 240.0,
    "text": "Everything!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.867,
    "endTime": 243.035,
    "text": "Even your paintings?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.16,
    "endTime": 246.288,
    "text": "Nobody would take them, so I had to eat them!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.921,
    "endTime": 257.048,
    "text": "There, there. You can come live with me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.841,
    "endTime": 260.636,
    "text": "Here you go, Squidward. You sleep in my bed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.761,
    "endTime": 265.641,
    "text": "OK, but just until I get a job. One day, two days tops."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.724,
    "endTime": 268.393,
    "text": "Nonsense, you stay as long as you need to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.73,
    "endTime": 273.023,
    "text": "Goodnight, my little angle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.148,
    "endTime": 274.858,
    "text": "Howdy ya'll!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.068,
    "endTime": 278.277,
    "text": "Wha-- What's this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.695,
    "endTime": 279.905,
    "text": "It's a party."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.489,
    "endTime": 281.573,
    "text": "For you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.157,
    "endTime": 283.282,
    "text": "For me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.408,
    "endTime": 285.327,
    "text": "It's your own little slice of Texas."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.452,
    "endTime": 288.372,
    "text": "Check it out, Sandy. We've got square dancing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.497,
    "endTime": 291.208,
    "text": "- Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow. - Giant barby Q's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.333,
    "endTime": 294.002,
    "text": "Homemade peas in a can pies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.127,
    "endTime": 297.589,
    "text": "And we got our very own ten gallon hats."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.007,
    "endTime": 300.0,
    "text": "So, what do you think? You gonna stay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.231,
    "endTime": 316.775,
    "text": "Don't cry anymore, Sandy. I'll go get your bag."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.491,
    "endTime": 327.24399999999997,
    "text": "I'm not crying, I'm laughing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.87,
    "endTime": 330.873,
    "text": "I appreciate what ya'll are trying to do, SpongeBob,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.956,
    "endTime": 333.709,
    "text": "but home isn't about barbeques and pecan pies,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.042,
    "endTime": 337.503,
    "text": "home is where you're surrounded by other critters that care about you."
  }
]